            "title": "The Emergence and Maintenance of Vector-Borne Diseases in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Province, and the Federally Administered Tribal Areas of Pakistan",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Nathan C.",
                    "lastName": "Nieto"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
