            "title": "Local knowledge on a cosmopolitan ﬁsh Ethnoecology of Pomatomus saltatrix (Pomatomidae) in Brazil and Australia",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "R A M",
                    "lastName": "Silvano"
